title: ---PENDING-- apartment, parking, yard, dishwasher, Utilities Included!
posting_body: ['*For more information or to set up a showing please reply with answers  to questions below*:', 'Second floor apartment in small 4 unit building with friendly long term neighbors.', 'Light and bright with windows overlooking garden yard', 'Great St. Paul location close to shopping, whole foods, restaurants, coffee shops, schools / colleges, parks, river, transportation, etc.', 'Wood floors, Ceramic Bath, Dishwasher, Onsite Laundry.', 'All you pay is rent (utilities included).', 'Sized for 1 or 2 people', 'Square footage is estimated.', 'Deposit = one months rent (may be more if pets or credit issues), 12 month lease to start.', 'No UD/eviction/criminal history or judgments and should have good credit, and verifiable income of 3 X rent', 'Some small pets may be allowed with pet agreements.', '*For more information or to set up a showing please reply with ALL below*:', '-YOUR FULL NAME(S), AGE(S)', '-WHEN YOU ARE LOOKING TO MOVE,', '-NUMBER OF PEOPLE, AND IF PETS, DESCRIBE IN DETAIL.', '-WHERE YOU ARE MOVING FROM, AND WHY ARE YOU MOVING.', '*Replies lacking this basic level of information may be considered spam or scam and deleted.*', '*We give showing priority to those that provide information and or complete our application first.', 'THANK YOU']
